column2: b'Ninja Hattori-kun Plus Perman: Ninja Kaijuu Jippou tai Miracle Tamago'

b"Crossover film featuring both of Motoo Abiko's work. Both casts gets wrapped up when an alien egg falls from the sky that becomes a monster seeking destruction of the Earth.\n\nIt was screened as a double feature with Doraemon: Nobita no Little Star Wars."
